Waylun lilmu_t_affifeen*a*
Alla_th_eena i_tha_ ikt_a_loo AAal_a_ a*l*nn_a_si yastawfoon*a*
Wa-i_tha_ k_a_loohum aw wazanoohum yukhsiroon*a*
Al_a_ ya\_th_\unnu ol_a_-ika annahum mabAAoothoon*a*
Liyawmin AAa\_th_\eem*in*
Yawma yaqoomu a*l*nn_a_su lirabbi alAA_a_lameen*a*
Kall_a_ inna kit_a_ba alfujj_a_ri lafee sijjeen*in*
Wam_a_ adr_a_ka m_a_ sijjeen*un*
Kit_a_bun marqoom*un*
Waylun yawma-i_th_in lilmuka_thth_ibeen*a*
Alla_th_eena yuka_thth_iboona biyawmi a*l*ddeen*i*
Wam_a_ yuka_thth_ibu bihi ill_a_ kullu muAAtadin atheem*in*
I_tha_ tutl_a_ AAalayhi _a_y_a_tun_a_ q_a_la as_at_eeru al-awwaleen*a*
Kall_a_ bal r_a_na AAal_a_ quloobihim m_a_ k_a_noo yaksiboon*a*
Kall_a_ innahum AAan rabbihim yawma-i_th_in lama_h_jooboon*a*
Thumma innahum la_sa_loo alja_h_eem*i*
Thumma yuq_a_lu h_atha_ alla_th_ee kuntum bihi tuka_thth_iboon*a*
Kall_a_ inna kit_a_ba al-abr_a_ri lafee AAilliyyeen*a*
Wam_a_ adr_a_ka m_a_ AAilliyyoon*a*
Kit_a_bun marqoom*un*
Yashhaduhu almuqarraboon*a*
Inna al-abr_a_ra lafee naAAeem*in*
AAal_a_ al-ar_a_-iki yan\_th_\uroon*a*
TaAArifu fee wujoohihim na_d_rata a*l*nnaAAeem*i*
Yusqawna min ra_h_eeqin makhtoom*in*
Khit_a_muhu miskun wafee _tha_lika falyatan_a_fasi almutan_a_fisoon*a*
Wamiz_a_juhu min tasneem*in*
AAaynan yashrabu bih_a_ almuqarraboon*a*
Inna alla_th_eena ajramoo k_a_noo mina alla_th_eena _a_manoo ya_dh_akoon*a*
Wa-i_tha_ marroo bihim yatagh_a_mazoon*a*
Wa-i_tha_ inqalaboo il_a_ ahlihimu inqalaboo fakiheen*a*
Wa-i_tha_ raawhum q_a_loo inna h_a_ol_a_-i la_da_lloon*a*
Wam_a_ orsiloo AAalayhim _ha_fi\_th_\een*a*
Fa*a*lyawma alla_th_eena _a_manoo mina alkuff_a_ri ya_dh_akoon*a*
AAal_a_ al-ar_a_-iki yan\_th_\uroon*a*
Hal thuwwiba alkuff_a_ru m_a_ k_a_noo yafAAaloon*a*
